lab.ts = ts(data=dataset$Value, frequency = 12, start=c(1985,3), end=c(2018,1))
plot(lab.ts, ylab=" ", xlab="")

plot(SMA(lab.ts, n=3))

plot(SMA(lab.ts, n=9))

, .

acf(lab.ts)

pacf(lab.ts)
